lemented powerful gamification technology and digital business transformation practices. Innovative agencies such as Perficient and EuroRSCG are bringing Badgeville-powered gamification solutions to their clients as a mission-critical part of customer and employee-facing engagement and loyalty going forward. Some of the leading technology companies in the world including Oracle, Callidus and Saba have deployed Badgeville technology to drive differentiation and value in their core go-to-market software offerings.” Badgeville’s strong success and growth across all parameters is indicative of the momentum gamification continues to build. While there are some naysayers following gamification in its hype cycle , gamification successes are relient on effective implementation and good design. Badgeville is certainly doing something right. Image by  Nicholas_T --- GSummit 2013 (April 16-18) is the only global event that brings together top experts in engaging design. Register now to see top experts share their secrets of how to create engagement and create key executive strategies for the enterprise, human resources, loyalty, and marketing at GSummit.com For being an awesome part of our Community, here's an additional $50 off your ticket purchase. Use code IMAWESOME at Registration. The post Industrial Strength: Badgeville Showed Triple-Digit Growth in 2012 appeared first on Gamification Co . 
